00:00:02.139 --> 00:00:07.890
I am sure somebody must have spoken before,
no?

00:00:07.890 --> 00:00:10.799
All right.

00:00:10.799 --> 00:00:20.720
You all have been seeking, and seeking the
truth about yourself.

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:24.550
Where does the truth lie?

00:00:24.550 --> 00:00:33.920
When are we the most truthful people?

00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:43.170
Where, at what point, we cannot deceive, whatever
we may try?

00:00:43.170 --> 00:00:50.750
When it is heartfelt.

00:00:50.750 --> 00:01:06.150
When it is our heart’s desire, then we always
try to go ahead with it.

00:01:06.150 --> 00:01:13.830
But it has to be heart’s desire not the
rationality, not the brain’s desire.

00:01:13.830 --> 00:01:19.710
Because you can make your brain understand.

00:01:19.710 --> 00:01:23.070
Your intelligence can be compromised.

00:01:23.070 --> 00:01:28.750
Whatever is heartfelt you want to do it.

00:01:28.750 --> 00:01:35.399
You cannot be satisfied without doing it.

00:01:35.399 --> 00:01:40.610
So, in the heart lies the truth.

00:01:40.610 --> 00:01:47.570
That is the Spirit that lies in your heart.

00:01:47.570 --> 00:01:53.610
But that is not in our conscious mind.

00:01:53.610 --> 00:01:56.840
We do not know how it manifests.

00:01:56.840 --> 00:02:11.459
We have heard that it is eternal, indestructible,
is the source of joy and is the attention

00:02:11.459 --> 00:02:12.629
of God.

00:02:12.629 --> 00:02:17.519
That’s what we have heard.

00:02:17.519 --> 00:02:28.030
All such things which are preached may be
regarded as hearsays.

00:02:28.030 --> 00:02:39.030
People might say, “What’s the proof that
there is a Spirit in our heart?”

00:02:39.030 --> 00:02:49.790
Thank God, people have discovered the heart
at least there, if not the Spirit!

00:02:49.790 --> 00:03:01.180
How are we to believe that there is Spirit
– that we have a dimension which is beyond

00:03:01.180 --> 00:03:08.489
this human dimension, which is the dimension
of the Spirit, the Spiritual dimension – by

00:03:08.489 --> 00:03:12.720
which we can feel the All-pervading Power
of Divine love?

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:21.940
It’s all being told to us by all the priests
of all the religions.

00:03:21.940 --> 00:03:23.720
Now where is that Spirit?

00:03:23.720 --> 00:03:30.110
Whether it resides in the heart or where?

00:03:30.110 --> 00:03:31.200
How are we to know?

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:32.230
How are we to believe?

00:03:32.230 --> 00:03:35.390
Or are we to deny all those people?

00:03:35.390 --> 00:03:40.370
Did they tell us lies about it?

00:03:40.370 --> 00:03:45.519
They may say, “You imagine, now, [that]
your awareness is that of the Spirit."

00:03:45.519 --> 00:03:47.760
By imagination you are not there!

00:03:47.760 --> 00:03:49.379
It’s just an imagination.

00:03:49.379 --> 00:03:55.080
Suddenly you find it was just a bubble and
whole thing has burst off.

00:03:55.080 --> 00:04:08.489
So today the questioning mind comes to a point,
to inquire: is there something called Spirit

00:04:08.489 --> 00:04:11.569
that we have to identify with?

00:04:11.569 --> 00:04:24.570
This inquiry itself is a seeking, because
you also do not know what is the meaning of

00:04:24.570 --> 00:04:27.470
your life?

00:04:27.470 --> 00:04:32.790
You also do not know why you were made a human
being?

00:04:32.790 --> 00:04:40.540
What was the need for the nature to create
human beings on this Earth?

00:04:40.540 --> 00:04:50.670
Why they took so much time to create it, evolve
us to this stage where we are called as human

00:04:50.670 --> 00:04:53.820
beings?

00:04:53.820 --> 00:04:59.380
Nobody asked the question why: the scientists
do not.

00:04:59.380 --> 00:05:07.930
Also the people who are so called religious
do not ask the question why, they just believed

00:05:07.930 --> 00:05:09.090
in it, “Have faith!

00:05:09.090 --> 00:05:11.470
Have faith!

00:05:11.470 --> 00:05:18.940
Faith is the only way you can go to God."

00:05:18.940 --> 00:05:20.290
Blind faith!

00:05:20.290 --> 00:05:27.920
