In the same way your Spirit has to come into
your conscious mind so that you know God in

00:22:59.670 --> 00:23:07.220
your conscious mind.

00:23:07.220 --> 00:23:12.330
I would like you people to ask me some questions,
the new people who have come and old people.

00:23:12.330 --> 00:23:15.570
If there are some questions I would like to
answer.

00:23:15.570 --> 00:23:21.540
But you see it’s such a big subject and
every time I have to go with the introduction.

00:23:21.540 --> 00:23:25.830
I thought somebody must have given you introduction
to you, but doesn’t matter there’s book

00:23:25.830 --> 00:23:28.179
which you can read and find out yourself.

00:23:28.179 --> 00:23:35.500
But it’s best to know, is to have it.

00:23:35.500 --> 00:23:39.300
Seeker: (inaudible)

00:23:39.300 --> 00:23:48.270
Shri Mataji: What can one do?

00:23:48.270 --> 00:23:51.549
Good idea.

00:23:51.549 --> 00:23:52.549
You got Realisation last time.

00:23:52.549 --> 00:24:04.100
The problem is, it’s a collective happening.

00:24:04.100 --> 00:24:09.910
Many people have to get Realisation and it’s
not individualistic.

00:24:09.910 --> 00:24:18.160
We are all part and parcel of the whole, so
if one finger is enlightened, that finger

00:24:18.160 --> 00:24:23.280
should try to enlighten another finger.

00:24:23.280 --> 00:24:31.780
That is the best way, best way because once
this finger tries that it gets its power more.

00:24:31.780 --> 00:24:37.070
Why should God give power to anyone who just
wants to keep it to himself?

00:24:37.070 --> 00:24:41.750
The power increases as you start giving it
to others.

00:24:41.750 --> 00:24:48.750
Like when you open one door no air will come
in, but if you open the other door the circulation

00:24:48.750 --> 00:24:49.750
starts.

00:24:49.750 --> 00:24:55.350
In the same way when you start giving it to
others – start raising the Kundalini; right

00:24:55.350 --> 00:24:57.130
now you can start.

00:24:57.130 --> 00:25:04.450
Just don’t be afraid, you can do it – you
will find immediately inside you will be coming

00:25:04.450 --> 00:25:05.450
up.

00:25:05.450 --> 00:25:11.600
Those who try to be exclusive and try to be
something great by doing everything at home

00:25:11.600 --> 00:25:13.800
and, “Especially for myself!”

00:25:13.800 --> 00:25:15.450
They are nowhere.

00:25:15.450 --> 00:25:20.260
I find such people have horrible drawbacks.

00:25:20.260 --> 00:25:27.170
Mix up with the other people: share it, share
it all the time and give Realisation to others.

00:25:27.170 --> 00:25:31.700
Those who have given Realisation to others
have come up very much.

00:25:31.700 --> 00:25:37.220
Those who think of others being realised,
come up much faster than the people who sit

00:25:37.220 --> 00:25:39.730
at home and meditate for five hours.

00:25:39.730 --> 00:25:42.309
There’s no need to meditate like that.

00:25:42.309 --> 00:25:46.470
At the most just to cleanse yourself you can
spend about ten, fifteen minutes.

00:25:46.470 --> 00:25:50.910
But there are many people whose attention
is only on themselves: “I must cleanse,

00:25:50.910 --> 00:25:59.429
I must cleanse I must do this,” such people
do not get very far in Sahaj Yog.

00:25:59.429 --> 00:26:05.190
Those people who try to do it for others,
talk to other people, work out much better.

00:26:05.190 --> 00:26:09.570
I would say Australians have done much better
than English have done.

00:26:09.570 --> 00:26:12.650
Maybe because of their temperaments, maybe.

00:26:12.650 --> 00:26:15.000
And they are not such closed people you see.

00:26:15.000 --> 00:26:23.090
For example they have their friends and there’s
no taboo on discussing religion with friends

00:26:23.090 --> 00:26:24.090
as it is in England.

00:26:24.090 --> 00:26:26.210
I think in England nobody discusses religion.

00:26:26.210 --> 00:26:31.700
They’ll discuss the pubs and all nonsense
and all filth, but not the religion.

00:26:31.700 --> 00:26:36.280
They are not supposed to: in etiquettes it
is prohibited I think.

00:26:36.280 --> 00:26:42.760
So naturally this taboo leads you nowhere,
because you can’t talk of Sahaj Yoga to

00:26:42.760 --> 00:26:44.250
your friends, who are there.

00:26:44.250 --> 00:26:54.340
If they come to your house, you can ask them
what are the new wines in the market or, something,

00:26:54.340 --> 00:26:57.059
such an ‘important’ thing they will talk
about.

00:26:57.059 --> 00:27:02.760
But you can’t talk about religion or your
experiences of Sahaj Yoga that’s the problem

00:27:02.760 --> 00:27:06.170
– it’s regarded as bad manners.

00:27:06.170 --> 00:27:12.980
Now the question is that, these things are
to be shared and that’s why the Sahaj Yoga

00:27:12.980 --> 00:27:16.700
you can only talk among Sahaj Yogis so it
[only] circulates among Sahaj Yogis.

00:27:16.700 --> 00:27:18.040
Nobody wants to hear about it.

00:27:18.040 --> 00:27:22.789
Even if you try to tell them they’ll say,”Oh
don’t tell us that we are not interested!”

00:27:22.789 --> 00:27:27.090
It’s a very funny thing.

00:27:27.090 --> 00:27:33.560
The other day I met a gentleman who had divorced
his wife, and she got her Realisation somewhere

00:27:33.560 --> 00:27:37.270
and he got Realisation somewhere and both
of them met in a group.

00:27:37.270 --> 00:27:38.900
She said, “How are you here?”

00:27:38.900 --> 00:27:40.290
He said, “How are you here?”

00:27:40.290 --> 00:27:42.150
She said, “We both got Realisation."

00:27:42.150 --> 00:27:45.140
She said, “But you never told me about this!”

00:27:45.140 --> 00:27:48.090
He said, “I didn’t want to discuss religion."

00:27:48.090 --> 00:27:51.830
So she said, “I also got Realisation I didn’t
want to discuss religion."

00:27:51.830 --> 00:27:55.780
Ultimately they discussed their divorce and
had a divorce, you see!

00:27:55.780 --> 00:27:59.100
And if they had just told them that both of
them are realised and they would have never

00:27:59.100 --> 00:28:03.760
divorced, because he thought this lady is
not a seeker so he divorced her, and she thought

00:28:03.760 --> 00:28:04.760
he was not.

00:28:04.760 --> 00:28:09.100
Even if they had felt each other’s vibrations
they would have been all right to know.

00:28:09.100 --> 00:28:13.170
But she got her Realisation in another place
and he got Realisation in another place, and

00:28:13.170 --> 00:28:16.419
they never knew that both are realised people
on the same plane.

00:28:16.419 --> 00:28:22.760
He thought she was very materialistic and
she thought that he was very materialistic.

00:28:22.760 --> 00:28:25.309
And then there was misunderstanding about
it.

00:28:25.309 --> 00:28:29.240
And they are not to discuss, one should not
say these things.

00:28:29.240 --> 00:28:33.130
Naturally everything ended up in a divorce
and now they want to marry again!

00:28:33.130 --> 00:28:39.450
This is the one of the reasons why, in this
country, I think Sahaj Yoga doesn’t work

00:28:39.450 --> 00:28:42.630
out because you are not supposed to tell anyone.

00:28:42.630 --> 00:28:48.950
At the most you may tell it to your children,
maybe, I don’t know, to your mother, father

00:28:48.950 --> 00:28:49.950
sometimes.

00:28:49.950 --> 00:28:53.470
And all such people who have tried have been
able to bring their relations here.

00:28:53.470 --> 00:28:55.690
But it’s only relations, not in friends.

00:28:55.690 --> 00:28:59.010
With friends you are not supposed to say anything.

00:28:59.010 --> 00:29:01.590
It’s a funny thing, isn’t it?

00:29:01.590 --> 00:29:03.030
This is the society!

00:29:03.030 --> 00:29:04.030
What to do now?

00:29:04.030 --> 00:29:15.039
I hope gradually it will change, when people
will know about these things.

00:29:15.039 --> 00:29:24.240
And in Australia what they do is to have programmes
for seven days.

00:29:24.240 --> 00:29:26.710
It is very interesting I have got this from
there.

00:29:26.710 --> 00:29:31.710
In the ashram they have seven days programme
and out of this one day they have a public

00:29:31.710 --> 00:29:32.710
programme.

00:29:32.710 --> 00:29:35.630
On this day every Sahaj Yogi is supposed to
bring four more.

00:29:35.630 --> 00:29:39.700
He’s not allowed to come unless and until
brings four more that day.

00:29:39.700 --> 00:29:46.870
And you have to bring four more you cannot
just come to Mothers programme and they can’t

00:29:46.870 --> 00:29:50.750
listen to my tapes or anything unless and
until they bring four more.

00:29:50.750 --> 00:29:55.890
But it is possible in Australia because I
found the people much more open you see and

00:29:55.890 --> 00:29:57.610
they are.

00:29:57.610 --> 00:30:01.620
I mean here, because of the climate may be
or we are frightened of others whatever it

00:30:01.620 --> 00:30:03.130
is, there are certain taboos.

00:30:03.130 --> 00:30:08.270
Like etiquettes, I think they don’t believe
much in etiquettes perhaps.

00:30:08.270 --> 00:30:13.390
Like here there was an announcement that:
now you need not to do courtesy because of

00:30:13.390 --> 00:30:17.040
tight clothes so you can just bow.

00:30:17.040 --> 00:30:23.150
Something like that may turn up now that you
can discuss about seeking, if not about religion,

00:30:23.150 --> 00:30:25.370
I hope so.

00:30:25.370 --> 00:30:28.929
And this may be one of the reason people just
can’t talk about it.

00:30:28.929 --> 00:30:32.210
But still whomsoever, whom you know, you should
try to tell them that: “I have an experience.

00:30:32.210 --> 00:30:36.720
I met such and such person and this and that."

00:30:36.720 --> 00:30:40.620
Immediately you will surprised your vibrations
will go up.

00:30:40.620 --> 00:30:51.120
It is like this, that bigger the room, the
bigger is the light provided for.

00:30:51.120 --> 00:30:58.270
If it is a smaller room then we don’t put
a big light, isn’t it?

00:30:58.270 --> 00:31:01.140
In the same way if you have a wider thing.

00:31:01.140 --> 00:31:07.580
There’s a one gentleman in India I told
you that he gave Realisation to ten thousand

00:31:07.580 --> 00:31:08.580
people.

00:31:08.580 --> 00:31:17.419
I must say that in Cambridge, Hillary and
Jim and Dawn have given Realisation to so

00:31:17.419 --> 00:31:19.690
many people, so many people.

00:31:19.690 --> 00:31:27.190
It’s interesting because there are Chilean
people, and the Chileans don’t believe in

00:31:27.190 --> 00:31:32.460
such etiquettes so it has worked with them.

00:31:32.460 --> 00:31:36.110
Maybe one day this may work out here when
we’ll talk to others.

00:31:36.110 --> 00:31:44.059
So this is the only way you can really grow.

00:31:44.059 --> 00:31:46.789
Seeker: (Inaudible)

00:31:46.789 --> 00:31:58.130
Shri Mataji: Oh of course it is very important.

00:31:58.130 --> 00:32:00.742
No that’s true you have to cleanse yourself
also.

00:32:00.742 --> 00:32:03.340
There’s a way and method.

00:32:03.340 --> 00:32:07.670
I must circulate that, it’s a beautiful
thing they have written down these Australian:

00:32:07.670 --> 00:32:10.909
how they cleanse themselves, how they clear
out there chakras.

00:32:10.909 --> 00:32:12.470
That is very important.

00:32:12.470 --> 00:32:18.220
Of course you have to clean, [but] say supposing
you clean your car every day and you don’t

00:32:18.220 --> 00:32:19.220
move out.

00:32:19.220 --> 00:32:21.140
After sometime it will become a junk.

00:32:21.140 --> 00:32:23.370
It’s like that.

00:32:23.370 --> 00:32:28.340
You are cleaning yourself for what?

00:32:28.340 --> 00:32:29.750
What is the purpose?

00:32:29.750 --> 00:32:36.780
Every day we are cleaning, say the house and
everything and not even a rat comes in then

00:32:36.780 --> 00:32:39.380
what’s the use of such a house?

00:32:39.380 --> 00:32:50.920
If we clean all the lamps it should give light
otherwise what’s the use of cleaning?

00:32:50.920 --> 00:32:51.960
It must have a purpose.

00:32:51.960 --> 00:32:54.490
You must have a purpose.

00:32:54.490 --> 00:32:59.400
Otherwise some people are just meditating,
meditating for what, I just don’t understand,

00:32:59.400 --> 00:33:00.730
why are they meditating?

00:33:00.730 --> 00:33:01.730
For what?

00:33:01.730 --> 00:33:05.140
In all these gurus, they just say, “Oh you
go home and meditate."

00:33:05.140 --> 00:33:06.140
But do what?

00:33:06.140 --> 00:33:10.990
“Next time bring all the money to me and
again you go home and meditate."

00:33:10.990 --> 00:33:15.320
Then if money is finished, “Now sell your
house bring all the money to me and meditate."

00:33:15.320 --> 00:33:19.700
Then that is done then, “Sell your car,
sell everything, you stand on the streets

00:33:19.700 --> 00:33:20.710
and meditate."

00:33:20.710 --> 00:33:24.440
This is not the way!

00:33:24.440 --> 00:33:25.440
(Laughing)

00:33:25.440 --> 00:33:31.280
It has become a sort of a pass time for people
instead of going to pubs, maybe it is expensive,

00:33:31.280 --> 00:33:32.280
better meditate.

00:33:32.280 --> 00:33:35.090
It’s something like that you know.

00:33:35.090 --> 00:33:38.570
It has no meaning to this meditation.

00:33:38.570 --> 00:33:44.010
Meditation is that you have to be in meditation
when you see that these centres are in problem,

00:33:44.010 --> 00:33:50.320
you cleanse them understandingly, purify them
and then use it for a purpose of giving it

00:33:50.320 --> 00:33:51.929
to others.

00:33:51.929 --> 00:33:58.320
And once you start doing it, it works better,
your instrument works much, much better.

00:33:58.320 --> 00:33:59.789
It’s a dual way of doing things.

00:33:59.789 --> 00:34:00.789
All right?

00:34:00.789 --> 00:34:09.260
Seeker: Can the realised people recognise
other people who are realised?

00:34:09.260 --> 00:34:26.819
Shri Mataji: Of course, minimum of minimum.

00:34:26.819 --> 00:34:29.210
Same Seeker: (Inaudible)

00:34:29.210 --> 00:34:34.399
Shri Mataji: No I wouldn’t say that.

00:34:34.399 --> 00:34:41.309
You see, Realisation is that, first it’s
a linear movement of the Kundalini, so it

00:34:41.309 --> 00:34:43.980
depends on what chakras are catching.

00:34:43.980 --> 00:34:46.020
Supposing somebody has a Nabhi problem.

00:34:46.020 --> 00:34:51.800
So you can’t say it’s a different stage
but he has a Nabhi problem, a particular problem.

00:34:51.800 --> 00:34:55.139
Somebody has some other problem, like that.

00:34:55.139 --> 00:35:01.539
But the other stage comes in when we would
say that once the first stage is called as

00:35:01.539 --> 00:35:06.150
Nirvichar Samadhi that you achieve even before
Realisation, I mean you achieve but you do

00:35:06.150 --> 00:35:07.499
not retain it.

00:35:07.499 --> 00:35:13.430
When the Kundalini crosses over this centre
(of Agnya) then this Nirvichar Samadhi -means

00:35:13.430 --> 00:35:15.130
thoughtless awareness – settles in.

00:35:15.130 --> 00:35:19.890
But with this you can cure people but cannot
raise Kundalini.

00:35:19.890 --> 00:35:23.670
But when it pierces through then you can raise
the Kundalini of other people.

00:35:23.670 --> 00:35:29.640
But when it is settled down nicely, and when
you are absolutely without any doubts, it’s

00:35:29.640 --> 00:35:36.500
a state, it’s a state of mind that comes
into you where you are absolutely doubtlessly

00:35:36.500 --> 00:35:38.319
aware.

00:35:38.319 --> 00:35:44.619
When that happens then only we expose you
to new experiences, before that we do not.

00:35:44.619 --> 00:35:52.799
That’s a thing we have a little, we should
say, a little group of people where you have

00:35:52.799 --> 00:35:56.000
to go up to Nirvikalpa Samadhi.

00:35:56.000 --> 00:36:02.349
Unless and until you go to that stage you
cannot be exposed to new experiences because

00:36:02.349 --> 00:36:05.269
you may shun it.

00:36:05.269 --> 00:36:09.200
Because the truth can be quite difficult for
you.

00:36:09.200 --> 00:36:16.969
So that’s the second stage we can say, where
you are exposed to those new experiences.

00:36:16.969 --> 00:36:22.410
But first stage is to become thoughtlessly
aware with the vibrations.

00:36:22.410 --> 00:36:25.170
But you can give Realisation to others, you
can give.

00:36:25.170 --> 00:36:30.930
But Nirvikalpa is a different thing that:
whatever may happen you know that this is

00:36:30.930 --> 00:36:33.450
the truth, whatever may happen.

00:36:33.450 --> 00:36:35.539
That stage is to be achieved.

00:36:35.539 --> 00:36:36.890
It’s a stage.

00:36:36.890 --> 00:36:44.390
It’s a very high stage I would say where
you are so sensitive to things that immediately

00:36:44.390 --> 00:36:50.450
you know what is negativity, from where it
is coming, how the attack is coming, how others

00:36:50.450 --> 00:36:51.480
are affected.

00:36:51.480 --> 00:36:58.349
We have a quite a lot of them among here also
people and then you are exposed to new experiences

00:36:58.349 --> 00:37:02.529
better, and then you rise in there – that’s
the Nirvikalpa Samadhi.

00:37:02.529 --> 00:37:08.589
Then the complete Self-realisation comes in,
in a person, where he’s not bothered about

00:37:08.589 --> 00:37:19.469
catching from anyone or getting any catches
or anything and he goes on with a very confident

00:37:19.469 --> 00:37:22.200
attitude towards Sahaj Yoga.

00:37:22.200 --> 00:37:26.200
I mean he is not bothered whether, “I am
catching or something is happening.

00:37:26.200 --> 00:37:28.289
I will not see that person."

00:37:28.289 --> 00:37:29.809
That sort of stage.

00:37:29.809 --> 00:37:35.049
And we have some people on that stage who
are, I can say, self-realised fully.

00:37:35.049 --> 00:37:38.180
They can control even elements.

00:37:38.180 --> 00:37:41.059
There are people, we have got such people.

00:37:41.059 --> 00:37:43.219
Beyond that is the stage of God’s-realisation.

00:37:43.219 --> 00:37:46.309
That’s again in three stages works out.

00:37:46.309 --> 00:37:53.710
But just now let’s start from the very beginning
and it will work out I am sure now.

00:37:53.710 --> 00:38:03.009
Now I’ve been working here for seven years
and actually some of these people who are

00:38:03.009 --> 00:38:09.060
at Nirvikalpa have not been here even for
a year.

00:38:09.060 --> 00:38:11.059
So it can work very fast.

00:38:11.059 --> 00:38:18.029
As the people grow in number, these stages
also grow in maturity very fast.

00:38:18.029 --> 00:38:23.140
You mature much faster as the people are more.

00:38:23.140 --> 00:38:28.019
When there were few people you should know
that I had six people I was struggling with

00:38:28.019 --> 00:38:31.680
them for four years in England.

00:38:31.680 --> 00:38:39.079
Even in India the first disciples who got
Realisation were with me for two years continuously

00:38:39.079 --> 00:38:42.250
and then they got Realisation, the first twelve.

00:38:42.250 --> 00:38:45.410
It’s like that.

00:38:45.410 --> 00:38:54.390
Now you know, everybody, all of you, are giving
Realisation.

00:38:54.390 --> 00:38:56.319
Seeker: (Unclear)

00:38:56.319 --> 00:39:02.109
Shri Mataji: Oh dynamic, absolutely dynamic.

00:39:02.109 --> 00:39:05.880
Efficiency is too simple a word.

00:39:05.880 --> 00:39:09.390
You just become dynamic.

00:39:09.390 --> 00:39:11.849
Because a dynamic starts flowing through.

00:39:11.849 --> 00:39:14.450
You don’t know how things work out.

00:39:14.450 --> 00:39:15.869
It’s amazing!

00:39:15.869 --> 00:39:20.119
It’s amazing how things work out.

00:39:20.119 --> 00:39:32.269
Then all the forces which are dynamic, Divine
start their play in every way, material way

00:39:32.269 --> 00:39:35.940
also, I must say.

00:39:35.940 --> 00:39:39.719
Like London Sahaj Yogis wanted to have some
houses.

00:39:39.719 --> 00:39:42.479
They said, “All right."

00:39:42.479 --> 00:39:47.420
Now they have so many houses they don’t
know what to do them!

00:39:47.420 --> 00:39:55.589
(Laughter) This is the condition: they don’t
know what to do, from where to get people

00:39:55.589 --> 00:39:56.589
to house them.

00:39:56.589 --> 00:39:58.310
This is the condition.

00:39:58.310 --> 00:40:04.359
While nobody can get a house like that for
one year absolutely free or two years absolutely

00:40:04.359 --> 00:40:06.880
free, a house that is just to be painted or
something.

00:40:06.880 --> 00:40:08.880
And many houses like that.

00:40:08.880 --> 00:40:12.420
They are getting one after so many houses
[that] they don’t know what to do with that!

00:40:12.420 --> 00:40:18.569
I mean, a person will have to live in three
houses if we have to divide them!

00:40:18.569 --> 00:40:19.569
(Laughter)

00:40:19.569 --> 00:40:28.329
And a lady came to me she said I am told that
houses are only given to Sahaj Yogis so I

00:40:28.329 --> 00:40:29.579
want to join Sahaj Yoga.

00:40:29.579 --> 00:40:31.150
I said, “Very good idea!

00:40:31.150 --> 00:40:36.160
But first you must get your Realisation, otherwise
the Sahaj Yogis won’t have you anywhere

00:40:36.160 --> 00:40:37.160
near.

00:40:37.160 --> 00:40:39.779
They don’t want people with bad vibrations.

00:40:39.779 --> 00:40:43.619
So you have to get your Realisation."

00:40:43.619 --> 00:40:50.369
I mean, it’s just a one of the small instances
but there are a thousand and one because it

00:40:50.369 --> 00:40:51.369
becomes dynamic.

00:40:51.369 --> 00:40:52.579
Your desire get enlightened.

00:40:52.579 --> 00:40:59.809
First of all your desires become sensible,
you have wise desires and they get enlightened:

00:40:59.809 --> 00:41:03.240
means you desire and you get it.

00:41:03.240 --> 00:41:05.089
You are amazed!

00:41:05.089 --> 00:41:06.930
Lady Seeker: (Unclear)

00:41:06.930 --> 00:41:11.180
Shri Mataji: It is fantastic!

00:41:11.180 --> 00:41:16.150
Can you stand up please?

00:41:16.150 --> 00:41:19.709
I can’t hear you.

00:41:19.709 --> 00:41:20.709
You please stand up here.

00:41:20.709 --> 00:41:21.809
Australian Seeker: It’s described how the
Holy Spirit came on the Apostles in the Acts

00:41:21.809 --> 00:41:32.140
of The Apostles, is that the same thing that
you are talking about?

00:41:32.140 --> 00:41:38.099
Shri Mataji: I don’t think that was Holy
Ghost.

00:41:38.099 --> 00:41:43.729
These apostles were also, the less said the
better!

00:41:43.729 --> 00:41:47.589
You will know about them.

00:41:47.589 --> 00:41:54.569
They were not realised, they never believed
in Christ till He got His resurrection which

00:41:54.569 --> 00:41:59.160
they saw with their eyes they never believed
in Him.

00:41:59.160 --> 00:42:01.239
You will know more about them.

00:42:01.239 --> 00:42:06.369
I don’t want to go into any controversies
but that’s not the way.

00:42:06.369 --> 00:42:08.140
You see, there are many people you have seen
now.

00:42:08.140 --> 00:42:11.739
The other day I saw in BBC a man who is painting
like Van Gogh.

00:42:11.739 --> 00:42:16.319
And he can say that, “I have got Holy Ghost
on me!”

00:42:16.319 --> 00:42:19.539
That’s not the way, it’s a [dead] spirit.

00:42:19.539 --> 00:42:21.440
Why God should make him paint like him?

00:42:21.440 --> 00:42:30.859
If God has to give you something, He has to
give you something that you cannot do.

00:42:30.859 --> 00:42:37.109
If you start speaking many languages, may
be so many dead spirits must have entered

00:42:37.109 --> 00:42:38.109
into people.

00:42:38.109 --> 00:42:40.279
There are many people who do that way.

00:42:40.279 --> 00:42:44.140
They just start talking so many languages,
there are spirits in them.

00:42:44.140 --> 00:42:45.509
What is there to speak many languages?

00:42:45.509 --> 00:42:46.569
What is so great?

00:42:46.569 --> 00:42:50.950
We have in India one gentleman who can speak
twenty-eight languages, so what?

00:42:50.950 --> 00:42:55.229
He’s not a realised-soul by any chance.

00:42:55.229 --> 00:42:56.780
But how to talk [to them]?

00:42:56.780 --> 00:43:03.329
They were just ordinary fishermen and they
would not listen.

00:43:03.329 --> 00:43:06.979
You see, they were thinking they were obliging
Christ.

00:43:06.979 --> 00:43:11.859
Every day there were list of relations who
were sick, who were brought to Christ, and

00:43:11.859 --> 00:43:27.609
[it was] a big problem you know, a very tragic
thing, horrible.

00:43:27.609 --> 00:43:34.240
People are much wiser now.

00:43:34.240 --> 00:43:40.670
It’s very different now.

00:43:40.670 --> 00:43:46.299
How could you talk to these people about Kundalini,
could you?

00:43:46.299 --> 00:43:50.609
This is what happened with everyone who came
on this Earth.

00:43:50.609 --> 00:43:52.579
Even Mohammad Sahib.

00:43:52.579 --> 00:43:54.670
They know how to butcher.

00:43:54.670 --> 00:44:00.109
You see, these people are not seekers and
they came to Christ.

00:44:00.109 --> 00:44:02.230
They were not seekers.

00:44:02.230 --> 00:44:05.890
If they were…I must say John was the best
among [them].

00:44:05.890 --> 00:44:10.339
Even Mathew, he argued so much about the Immaculate
Conception.

00:44:10.339 --> 00:44:14.420
You see, you don’t know what was all that.

00:44:14.420 --> 00:44:15.420
Forget it!

00:44:15.420 --> 00:44:16.789
You’ll know about them later on.

00:44:16.789 --> 00:44:19.039
It is better you see now, to yourself.

00:44:19.039 --> 00:44:21.519
Now I am before you, all right, forget about
them.

00:44:21.519 --> 00:44:23.279
Let’s have it out.

00:44:23.279 --> 00:44:25.910
It’s not that same thing.

00:44:25.910 --> 00:44:30.050
You won’t be speaking many languages I can
assure you!

00:44:30.050 --> 00:44:31.050
(Laughing)

00:44:31.050 --> 00:44:37.259
But cold wind is the thing, that’s the thing.

00:44:37.259 --> 00:44:40.900
That’s very true.

00:44:40.900 --> 00:44:51.359
We had one experience of that: one gentleman
who was doing black magic, when, you say,

00:44:51.359 --> 00:44:57.069
he was ‘archbishop’ of black magic, he
came to Sahaj Yoga and he got his Realisation

00:44:57.069 --> 00:44:59.099
he got the cold wind.

00:44:59.099 --> 00:45:06.309
And after that all the cups and saucers in
his house started flying around and everything

00:45:06.309 --> 00:45:07.309
happening.

00:45:07.309 --> 00:45:12.700
I mean it has happen very recently, about
I think fifteen, twenty days back.

00:45:12.700 --> 00:45:18.380
And at about twelve o’clock in the night,
people from Brighton rang me at twelve o’clock

00:45:18.380 --> 00:45:20.589
in the night, “Mother horrible things happening!”

00:45:20.589 --> 00:45:22.070
I said, “What happened?”

00:45:22.070 --> 00:45:27.209
“We gave Realisation to one man and the
whole house is in a whirlwind!

00:45:27.209 --> 00:45:31.460
Everything is moving around and we don’t
know what to do and everything cracking!”

00:45:31.460 --> 00:45:33.089
“Oh God!”

00:45:33.089 --> 00:45:36.670
I said, “who is this gentleman whom you
gave Realisation?”

00:45:36.670 --> 00:45:41.019
He said, “He is very great in black magic
this and that."

00:45:41.019 --> 00:45:45.000
I said, “Why did you give him Realisation?”

00:45:45.000 --> 00:45:50.650
It’s a thing you know, they try to tempt,
because these spirits were around and they

00:45:50.650 --> 00:45:51.650
wanted to tempt him.

00:45:51.650 --> 00:45:54.680
They want to frighten also.

00:45:54.680 --> 00:45:58.990
Because he has been so much with them, they
don’t want to give them up.

00:45:58.990 --> 00:45:59.990
And these things happen.

00:45:59.990 --> 00:46:04.509
But that’s not the thing that we should
expect.

00:46:04.509 --> 00:46:08.289
There was a lady whom I gave Realisation.

00:46:08.289 --> 00:46:14.740
I told her that, “Because you are been indulging
into nonsensical things, your guru was a very

00:46:14.740 --> 00:46:19.979
big tantrik and he used to do all such tricks,
you may start doing that after Realisation

00:46:19.979 --> 00:46:21.519
also."

00:46:21.519 --> 00:46:25.789
So she said, “No, no, no, Mother I don’t
want all that, I want param, I want the reality,

00:46:25.789 --> 00:46:26.789
I don’t want that."

00:46:26.789 --> 00:46:29.390
I said, “But still it will happen.

00:46:29.390 --> 00:46:31.249
Somebody may try to tempt you so.

00:46:31.249 --> 00:46:34.829
Because they do not want you to be realised."

00:46:34.829 --> 00:46:37.869
And it happened to her!

00:46:37.869 --> 00:46:43.700
Rice started falling from her hand, and then
she took another turn.

00:46:43.700 --> 00:46:47.630
Ultimately she became a mad woman.

00:46:47.630 --> 00:46:50.380
So it is so.

00:46:50.380 --> 00:46:57.599
It can happen, but rarely, not so much if
you have not been a professional black magician

00:46:57.599 --> 00:47:05.880
or something, it will not happen.

00:47:05.880 --> 00:47:13.249
We have misunderstood many things and that’s
why it is necessary to know it and then understand.

00:47:13.249 --> 00:47:18.709
Because if I tell you something there would
be blockade and barrier in your mind.

00:47:18.709 --> 00:47:22.700
As it is people are brainwashed by so many
things.

00:47:22.700 --> 00:47:26.619
Like those who are Muslims don’t want to
look at Christ, they don’t want to hear.

00:47:26.619 --> 00:47:29.470
Those who are Christians don’t want to hear
about anybody else.

00:47:29.470 --> 00:47:33.789
Those who are Hindus, they don’t want to
know about anybody else.

00:47:33.789 --> 00:47:38.119
But Sahaj Yoga gives meaning to all of them.

00:47:38.119 --> 00:47:39.209
All them, are important.

00:47:39.209 --> 00:47:43.369
All of them.

00:47:43.369 --> 00:47:49.430
Every one is important for Sahaj Yoga and
they reside within us in those different chakras.

00:47:49.430 --> 00:47:51.869
It’s a very different thing.

00:47:51.869 --> 00:47:55.609
One has to first see and then judge.

00:47:55.609 --> 00:47:58.539
Not to judge about anything without seeing
it.

00:47:58.539 --> 00:48:05.479
But without seeing, whatever we judge may
not be correct.

00:48:05.479 --> 00:48:06.940
All right?

00:48:06.940 --> 00:48:09.220
Should we have the vibrations now?

00:48:09.220 --> 00:48:10.289
Let’s.

